# CLIP ChangeLog for clip-dev/clip-install-config

*clip-install-config-1.2.4 (23 Feb 2016)

  23 Feb 2016; ANSSI <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-install-config-1.2.4.ebuild, -clip-install-config-1.2.3.ebuild:
  Migrate from clip-tiny to clip-bare.

*clip-install-config-1.2.3 (26 Oct 2012)

  26 Oct 2012; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-install-config-1.2.3.ebuild, -clip-install-config-1.2.2.ebuild:
  Fix usbkeys.conf:R{O,W}_LEVELS format.

*clip-install-config-1.2.2 (03 Oct 2012)

  03 Oct 2012; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-install-config-1.2.2.ebuild, -clip-install-config-1.2.1.ebuild:
  Fix package list scroll bar visibility.

*clip-install-config-1.2.1 (09 Aug 2012)

  09 Aug 2012; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-install-config-1.2.1.ebuild, -clip-install-config-1.2.0.ebuild:
  Use list_optional.pl from clip-config-2.3.9+ instead of our own custom
  copy.

*clip-install-config-1.2.0 (16 Jul 2012)

  16 Jul 2012; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-install-config-1.2.0.ebuild, -clip-install-config-1.1.9.ebuild:
  Fix outdated defaults for config options.
  Update net-const configuration to reflect changes in internal addresses
  (no configurable address for RM_B/USER, dynamic addresses for other jails).
  Update optional package configuration to display categories.
  Support switching to a new configuration base directory on the fly.

*clip-install-config-1.1.9 (28 Dec 2011)

  28 Dec 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-install-config-1.1.9.ebuild, -clip-install-config-1.1.8.ebuild:
  Support new dynamic device attribution.

*clip-install-config-1.1.8 (14 Nov 2011)

  14 Nov 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-install-config-1.1.8.ebuild, -clip-install-config-1.1.7.ebuild:
  Add quotes for usbkeys.conf variables.

*clip-install-config-1.1.7 (22 Aug 2011)

  22 Aug 2011; Vincent Strubel <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
  +clip-install-config-1.1.7.ebuild, -clip-install-config-1.1.6.ebuild:
  Fix bug in user add/modify dialog that would zero out all RM 
  partition sizes on user accounts created for single jail CLIP
  configurations.

  06 Jul 2011; Mickaël Salaün <clipos@ssi.gouv.fr>
